00:23:26,500 --> 00:23:27,910
Because there are some things

288
00:23:27,910 --> 00:23:30,510
I have to relay to the Sword Wielder privately.

289
00:23:32,320 --> 00:23:32,950
All right.

290
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:43,420
[Shang]

291
00:23:53,500 --> 00:23:53,860
Gosh.

292
00:23:53,860 --> 00:23:54,470
Ouch!

293
00:23:54,530 --> 00:23:54,910
Ouch!

294
00:23:56,650 --> 00:23:57,240
Gosh.

295
00:23:57,430 --> 00:23:58,020
-Hurry.
-Young Master.

296
00:23:58,020 --> 00:23:58,330
Help him.

297
00:23:58,330 --> 00:23:59,380
-Help him.
-What are you doing here?

298
00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:00,920
Gosh. Get up.

299
00:24:01,060 --> 00:24:01,740
It's dirty.

300
00:24:01,760 --> 00:24:02,490
Are you okay?

301
00:24:02,830 --> 00:24:04,400
Thief! Give it back to me.

302
00:24:04,740 --> 00:24:05,980
How could you say that?

303
00:24:05,980 --> 00:24:07,540
You hit me first.

304
00:24:07,740 --> 00:24:08,630
Even if you're not a thief,

305
00:24:08,630 --> 00:24:09,700
you are blind.

306
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:11,080
Watch where you're going.

307
00:24:11,080 --> 00:24:11,480
Hey.

308
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:13,350
I'm your sister.

309
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:14,850
You can't be rude to me.

310
00:24:14,910 --> 00:24:16,460
You're not my sister.

311
00:24:16,860 --> 00:24:18,320
Mother hates you the most.

312
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:21,190
That's because

313
00:24:21,360 --> 00:24:23,270
your mother is not my mother.

314
00:24:23,650 --> 00:24:25,830
But your father is my father.

315
00:24:25,960 --> 00:24:27,510
So we are still siblings.

316
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:29,640
But my father said he doesn't like you too.

317
00:24:29,640 --> 00:24:30,750
He only likes me.

318
00:24:36,610 --> 00:24:37,430
Let’s go first.

319
00:24:37,430 --> 00:24:39,230
What kind of Lineage Head is she?

320
00:24:39,930 --> 00:24:42,260
I am the Lineage Head of the Shang Lineage.

321
00:24:42,900 --> 00:24:44,220
When I grow up,

322
00:24:44,220 --> 00:24:46,320
Father will make her return the position to me.

323
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:46,720
Humph.

324
00:24:47,690 --> 00:24:48,380
Ah.

325
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:50,790
Don't cry.

326
00:24:51,000 --> 00:24:51,780
Let's get up.

327
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:53,370
I'll take you to the clinic.

328
00:24:59,580 --> 00:25:00,800
Are you satisfied?

329
00:25:01,220 --> 00:25:01,990
About what?

330
00:25:02,370 --> 00:25:04,430
I made him kneel and apologize to you.

331
00:25:05,060 --> 00:25:06,620
So it's you!

332
00:25:07,450 --> 00:25:09,490
You're the best, Xiaohei.

333
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:10,500
Of course.

334
00:25:10,710 --> 00:25:11,780
I think about

335
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,190
serving you everyday.

336
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:15,670
But...

337
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:17,980
You've already forgotten about me recently.

338
00:25:17,980 --> 00:25:20,020
You don't even come look for me to do research.

339
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:20,590
Sigh.

340
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,850
All you do is chase after that man all day.

341
00:25:23,670 --> 00:25:25,130
His name is Jin Fan, right?

342
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:25,670
Humph.

343
00:25:25,900 --> 00:25:26,960
I'll remember him.

344
00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:28,260
As you can see,

345
00:25:28,820 --> 00:25:30,020
although I am

346
00:25:30,020 --> 00:25:31,910
in charge of everything in the Shang Lineage,

347
00:25:31,910 --> 00:25:33,670
no one takes me seriously.

348
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,100
See,

349
00:25:35,460 --> 00:25:37,460
no matter how good

350
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,990
or powerful the weapon I create is,

351
00:25:38,990 --> 00:25:40,780
my father won't even take another look.

352
00:25:40,780 --> 00:25:41,760
What's the use?

353
00:25:43,230 --> 00:25:45,030
It's better to be good to Jin Fan.

354
00:25:45,340 --> 00:25:46,600
At least

355
00:25:46,830 --> 00:25:48,090
he really loves me.

356
00:25:48,930 --> 00:25:50,020
I don't see it.

357
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:51,320
I only see you

358
00:25:51,340 --> 00:25:53,380
chasing after him all day long.

359
00:25:54,660 --> 00:25:55,930
What do you know?

360
00:25:57,230 --> 00:25:57,840
Gosh.

361
00:26:10,800 --> 00:26:11,830
Eldest Young Miss.

362
00:26:11,830 --> 00:26:12,670
Young Master Ziyu said

363
00:26:12,670 --> 00:26:13,990
this is the hill pear from this year.

364
00:26:13,990 --> 00:26:15,190
He knows you like them

365
00:26:15,380 --> 00:26:17,110
so he asked me to bring you some.

366
00:26:19,020 --> 00:26:20,080
Eldest Young Miss?

367
00:26:28,470 --> 00:26:29,530
Eldest Young Miss.

368
00:26:37,170 --> 00:26:38,630
You have such a high fever.

369
00:26:38,810 --> 00:26:40,540
Why is no one taking care of you?

370
00:26:41,850 --> 00:26:43,250
Where are your servants?

371
00:26:45,630 --> 00:26:47,160
I'll take you to the clinic.

372
00:27:28,680 --> 00:27:29,670
To be honest,

373
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:31,620
I've recovered.

374
00:27:32,020 --> 00:27:32,740
Say no more,

375
00:27:32,910 --> 00:27:33,970
take the medicine.

376
00:27:34,330 --> 00:27:35,460
I can't do as you say.

377
00:27:35,930 --> 00:27:36,930
It's not up to you.

378
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:38,980
My life is horrible. No!

379
00:27:45,810 --> 00:27:46,740
Wait for me then.

380
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:56,640
Just wait for me for a while here.

381
00:28:24,530 --> 00:28:26,530
Do you want your favorite hill pear?

382
00:28:26,670 --> 00:28:27,660
Then take the medicine too

383
00:28:27,660 --> 00:28:28,460
along with it.

384
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,820
It's bitter but sweet.

385
00:28:40,620 --> 00:28:42,050
Sweet but bitter.

386
00:28:42,870 --> 00:28:43,650
Is this

387
00:28:44,300 --> 00:28:45,390
the sweet and bitter

388
00:28:45,390 --> 00:28:46,670
taste of love

389
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:48,770
they talk about

390
00:28:49,510 --> 00:28:51,040
in romance novels?

391
00:28:58,540 --> 00:28:59,110
Goodbye.

392
00:29:11,210 --> 00:29:11,670
Good...

393
00:29:12,390 --> 00:29:13,060
Goodbye.

394
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:48,710
You're still young.

395
00:29:49,140 --> 00:29:50,540
How do I tell you about it?

396
00:29:50,670 --> 00:29:52,310
The relationship between men and women

397
00:29:52,310 --> 00:29:53,780
can't be explained

398
00:29:53,970 --> 00:29:55,160
in just a few words.

399
00:29:55,580 --> 00:29:56,590
You're talking nonsense again.

400
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:57,650
I'm older than you.

401
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,980
Your face may be bigger, but everything else is below me.

402
00:29:59,980 --> 00:30:02,120
You're a servant in the kitchen.

403
00:30:02,350 --> 00:30:03,610
If people find out that

404
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:05,140
you came here to look for me secretly,

405
00:30:05,140 --> 00:30:06,820
you'll be doomed.

406
00:30:06,850 --> 00:30:08,320
You didn't come looking for me

407
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:09,890
so I can only come look for you.

408
00:30:09,890 --> 00:30:10,820
You have no idea.

409
00:30:11,150 --> 00:30:12,900
So many terrible and scary things

410
00:30:12,900 --> 00:30:14,300
happened in the Gong family.

411
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:15,900
How can I tell you about them?

412
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,180
I am shocked,

413
00:30:17,390 --> 00:30:18,360
worried,

414
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:19,910
and scared.

415
00:30:20,550 --> 00:30:21,880
Tell me about it slowly.

416
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:23,790
I'll help you calm down.

417
00:30:24,050 --> 00:30:24,650
All right.

418
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:27,310
Let me stretch while I talk about it.

419
00:30:27,670 --> 00:30:29,240
Here's what happened.

420
00:30:55,110 --> 00:30:55,990
What's wrong?

421
00:30:56,930 --> 00:30:58,660
You look pale.

422
00:31:01,010 --> 00:31:02,870
I just came back from the back hill

423
00:31:03,090 --> 00:31:04,520
and I caught a cold.

424
00:31:05,250 --> 00:31:06,470
What a good time to

425
00:31:08,070 --> 00:31:09,350
catch a cold.

426
00:31:09,770 --> 00:31:11,300
I wish I can catch a cold too.

427
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:14,230
My internal organs are all burning up.

428
00:31:18,990 --> 00:31:20,950
This painting is so vivid.

429
00:31:22,020 --> 00:31:23,680
If you have the time to do this,

430
00:31:23,970 --> 00:31:26,450
why not spend it on drawing more maps of the Gong residence

431
00:31:26,450 --> 00:31:28,380
and the distribution of the posts?

432
00:31:30,950 --> 00:31:32,480
It's none of your business.

433
00:31:37,990 --> 00:31:38,830
Speaking of,

434
00:31:38,930 --> 00:31:40,820
Gong Ziyu cares so much about you.

435
00:31:41,260 --> 00:31:42,840
You and Jin Fan

436
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:45,040
should be pretty close too, right?

437
00:31:45,300 --> 00:31:47,030
That has nothing to do with you.

438
00:31:54,460 --> 00:31:55,430
I didn't use to.

439
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:57,090
But now it does.

440
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:00,780
I need you to get close to Jin Fan

441
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:03,060
and take something from him.

442
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:05,410
I'm unable to help.

443
00:32:05,850 --> 00:32:07,150
Go get it yourself.

444
00:32:11,390 --> 00:32:12,650
Are you unable to help,

445
00:32:13,220 --> 00:32:14,880
or that you don't want to help?

446
00:32:15,380 --> 00:32:16,180
I'm unable,

447
00:32:17,170 --> 00:32:18,200
nor do I want to.

448
00:32:19,630 --> 00:32:20,550
You still

449
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:23,020
owe me a favor from last time.

450
00:32:23,810 --> 00:32:24,420
What now?

451
00:32:25,030 --> 00:32:26,630
You don't want to pay me back?

452
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:29,500
I can repay you,

453
00:32:30,470 --> 00:32:32,400
but you're trying to get me killed.

454
00:32:33,500 --> 00:32:35,660
You want me to steal something from Jin Fan.

455
00:32:35,660 --> 00:32:38,260
If it turns out badly, I might even lose my life.

456
00:32:39,590 --> 00:32:42,390
Didn't you just deliver medicine to Gong Yuanzhi?

457
00:32:42,610 --> 00:32:44,270
Then you must know how skilled

458
00:32:44,970 --> 00:32:46,400
Jin Fan is at fighting.

459
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:48,030
I know.

460
00:32:49,550 --> 00:32:51,900
So Jin Fan is definitely not so simple.

461
00:32:52,450 --> 00:32:53,670
He's too strong

462
00:32:54,290 --> 00:32:55,220
to be

463
00:32:55,390 --> 00:32:56,920
just a Green Jade Guardian.

464
00:32:57,740 --> 00:32:59,070
I've fought him before.

465
00:32:59,820 --> 00:33:00,850
Although I won,

466
00:33:02,150 --> 00:33:03,770
but when he fought me,

467
00:33:04,270 --> 00:33:06,200
he didn't even use 30% of his power.

468
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,850
Since he let you win,

469
00:33:08,790 --> 00:33:10,240
isn't it more convenient for you

470
00:33:10,240 --> 00:33:11,420
to steal it?

471
00:33:12,110 --> 00:33:13,060
Shangguan Qian.

472
00:33:14,650 --> 00:33:17,050
Do you think I don’t know what you want?

473
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:23,350
You are

474
00:33:23,900 --> 00:33:25,390
quite well-informed.

475
00:33:26,170 --> 00:33:28,770
You want that half of Jin Fan's medical record.

476
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:30,920
The thing I lost

477
00:33:32,260 --> 00:33:34,520
was the medical record of Ziyu's mother,

478
00:33:34,720 --> 00:33:36,520
Lady Lan, during her pregnancy.

479
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:41,720
If I help you steal the medical record,

480
00:33:42,110 --> 00:33:43,790
I'm helping Gong Shangjue

481
00:33:43,820 --> 00:33:47,450
drag Gong Ziyu down from the position of his position as the Sword Wielder.

482
00:33:47,450 --> 00:33:49,050
My mission at the Gong family

483
00:33:49,380 --> 00:33:50,900
will then fail.

484
00:33:52,870 --> 00:33:54,090
I understand now.

485
00:33:54,620 --> 00:33:57,220
Gong Ziyu's background has always been a mystery.

486
00:33:57,220 --> 00:33:58,350
This medical record

487
00:33:58,380 --> 00:34:01,780
can prove that Gong Ziyu is not Gong Hongyu's biological son.

488
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:03,420
Indeed...

489
00:34:04,430 --> 00:34:07,120
This concerns Gong Ziyu's position as the Sword Wielder.

490
00:34:07,120 --> 00:34:08,449
The thing you need to get

491
00:34:09,409 --> 00:34:10,810
is half a medical record.

492
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:13,210
As to its content and purpose,

493
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,730
don't ask what you shouldn't ask,

494
00:34:15,730 --> 00:34:17,790
and don't look at what you shouldn't.

495
00:34:18,310 --> 00:34:21,040
I didn't know the content of this medical record.

496
00:34:22,070 --> 00:34:24,130
Thank you for answering my question.

497
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,360
Looks like

498
00:34:27,010 --> 00:34:28,810
all the more I need to get it then.

499
00:34:30,389 --> 00:34:31,050
Stop there.

500
00:34:35,610 --> 00:34:36,780
If you get it,

501
00:34:37,770 --> 00:34:38,860
then I'll lose.

502
00:34:44,030 --> 00:34:45,080
My mission

503
00:34:45,580 --> 00:34:47,440
has a higher priority than yours.

504
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:49,520
You're but a Chi assassin.

505
00:34:49,889 --> 00:34:51,130
Just lose.

506
00:34:51,780 --> 00:34:53,710
There's no difference in priority

507
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:54,980
in Wufeng missions.

508
00:35:09,050 --> 00:35:10,710
The same level as me?

509
00:35:11,740 --> 00:35:13,270
No difference in priority?

510
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,880
Chi are pawns to start with.

511
00:35:16,090 --> 00:35:17,250
You'd be lucky

512
00:35:18,250 --> 00:35:19,810
to be able to help me.

513
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:32,160
Sister Yun.

514
00:35:34,410 --> 00:35:36,180
If you help me succeed,

515
00:35:37,750 --> 00:35:39,660
and I help Gong Shangjue succeed

516
00:35:40,900 --> 00:35:42,370
and gain his trust,

517
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:48,230
I'll be one step closer to success.

518
00:35:49,270 --> 00:35:50,900
After I succeed

519
00:35:51,870 --> 00:35:53,890
and return to Wufeng to receive the reward,

520
00:35:53,890 --> 00:35:55,800
I'll put in a good word for you.

521
00:35:59,310 --> 00:36:00,930
If you don't help me today,

522
00:36:01,750 --> 00:36:03,680
don't blame me for being ruthless.

523
00:36:23,030 --> 00:36:24,310
You're making cakes?

524
00:36:24,650 --> 00:36:25,170
Yes.

525
00:36:25,950 --> 00:36:27,480
Bitter gourd and mulberry?

526
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:28,980
What kind of combination is this?

527
00:36:28,980 --> 00:36:30,840
Don't get a tummy upset from this.

528
00:36:31,030 --> 00:36:32,060
It's a delicacy from my hometown.

529
00:36:32,060 --> 00:36:33,990
For everyone to try something new.

530
00:36:39,140 --> 00:36:39,710
Miss Yun.

531
00:36:40,740 --> 00:36:42,230
Where is the food you left for Guardian Jin?

532
00:36:42,230 --> 00:36:43,070
He just came back.

533
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:44,460
I have to deliver it to him.

534
00:36:44,460 --> 00:36:45,280
It's here.

535
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:49,230
Wait.

536
00:36:54,960 --> 00:36:56,830
Guardian Jin has been working hard lately.

537
00:36:56,830 --> 00:36:58,640
Bring him some cakes.

538
00:37:00,130 --> 00:37:00,470
Yes.

539
00:37:12,590 --> 00:37:13,640
Jin Fan was fine.

540
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:15,550
Why is he suddenly vomiting and having diarrheas?

541
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:16,200
Right.

542
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:17,750
I also found it strange.

543
00:37:18,070 --> 00:37:20,240
Could he have been poisoned

544
00:37:20,430 --> 00:37:21,980
without knowing when he fought with Young Master Yuanzhi?

545
00:37:21,980 --> 00:37:22,970
I'm so mad.

546
00:37:23,180 --> 00:37:24,730
If anything happens to Jinfan,

547
00:37:24,730 --> 00:37:26,260
I'll go and blow up... Gosh.

548
00:37:26,330 --> 00:37:28,060
I'll go and blow up Zhi Lineage.

549
00:37:29,150 --> 00:37:31,120
Do not be anxious, Eldest Young Miss.

550
00:37:31,120 --> 00:37:32,400
I am so anxious.

551
00:37:32,550 --> 00:37:33,470
But it doesn't matter.

552
00:37:33,470 --> 00:37:34,860
I brought my own Herb Elixir.

553
00:37:34,860 --> 00:37:36,190
Jin Fan can use it later.

554
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:40,220
Jin Fan!

555
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:44,380
Are you all right

556
00:37:44,380 --> 00:37:46,100
after being bitten by that poisonous insect?

557
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:47,280
What are you doing?

558
00:37:47,340 --> 00:37:47,930
Ouch!

559
00:37:50,090 --> 00:37:51,690
You have an ulterior motive.

560
00:37:51,730 --> 00:37:52,660
I'm really fine.

561
00:37:52,800 --> 00:37:53,640
Nonsense.

562
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,200
How can you be fine?

563
00:37:55,300 --> 00:37:56,060
You vomited.

564
00:37:56,290 --> 00:37:57,260
I've known you for so long,

565
00:37:57,260 --> 00:37:59,610
you haven't even sneezed before.

566
00:38:02,830 --> 00:38:04,680
You are the one who got bitten by

567
00:38:04,930 --> 00:38:06,460
Gong Yuanzhi's poisonous insects.

568
00:38:06,460 --> 00:38:08,440
I have to check if you are okay.

569
00:38:09,020 --> 00:38:10,750
That despicable Gong Yuanzhi

570
00:38:10,910 --> 00:38:12,220
is full of schemes.

571
00:38:12,550 --> 00:38:14,110
I'm afraid you won't even feel anything

572
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:16,170
when you have been eaten whole by him!

573
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:18,700
Eldest Young Miss,

