00:52:37,470 --> 00:52:38,860
how did Gong Shangjue

856
00:52:39,130 --> 00:52:40,140
pass this test?

857
00:52:41,750 --> 00:52:43,080
He has both persistence

858
00:52:43,480 --> 00:52:44,540
and capabilities.

859
00:52:45,260 --> 00:52:46,520
It's only natural that

860
00:52:47,550 --> 00:52:48,680
he passed this test.

861
00:52:50,200 --> 00:52:51,800
He dived to the end of the pool

862
00:52:51,920 --> 00:52:53,180
with his persistence.

863
00:52:54,590 --> 00:52:56,210
At the same time, with his strong internal skill,

864
00:52:56,210 --> 00:52:58,470
he controlled his breathing perfectly.

865
00:52:59,820 --> 00:53:00,940
After he got the iron box

866
00:53:00,940 --> 00:53:02,560
and emerged from the surface of the pool,

867
00:53:02,560 --> 00:53:04,220
he was still extremely sober,

868
00:53:04,510 --> 00:53:07,310
and sustained just some superficial frostbites.

869
00:53:08,860 --> 00:53:09,640
Did you

870
00:53:10,060 --> 00:53:12,260
teach him the Three Forms of Snow Saber?

871
00:53:12,330 --> 00:53:13,260
Did he master it?

872
00:53:13,960 --> 00:53:15,020
We won't know that.

873
00:53:17,740 --> 00:53:18,730
I must learn it

874
00:53:19,340 --> 00:53:20,400
and pay him a visit.

875
00:53:22,370 --> 00:53:23,310
I didn't expect

876
00:53:23,980 --> 00:53:25,060
the crybaby

877
00:53:25,350 --> 00:53:26,950
has become the Sword Wielder

878
00:53:27,890 --> 00:53:30,540
and took on the responsibility of the Gong family.

879
00:53:30,540 --> 00:53:31,720
You flatter me.

880
00:53:36,130 --> 00:53:38,190
After leaving the back hill that day,

881
00:53:38,500 --> 00:53:39,890
Elder Xue took me home.

882
00:53:41,360 --> 00:53:43,360
Father locked me up for three months

883
00:53:44,150 --> 00:53:46,150
and forced me to practice every day.

884
00:53:47,220 --> 00:53:49,300
He had high hopes for you.

885
00:53:52,010 --> 00:53:52,710
Yes.

886
00:53:54,010 --> 00:53:55,100
I understand now.

887
00:53:58,000 --> 00:53:58,930
Unfortunately,

888
00:54:01,320 --> 00:54:02,720
I only understood it now.

889
00:54:09,930 --> 00:54:11,260
Have you ever blamed me?

890
00:54:11,780 --> 00:54:12,870
I never came to look for you

891
00:54:12,870 --> 00:54:14,220
since then.

892
00:54:16,050 --> 00:54:17,180
I promised

893
00:54:17,350 --> 00:54:18,550
to take you to the sea,

894
00:54:18,950 --> 00:54:19,950
to view lanterns,

895
00:54:20,350 --> 00:54:21,430
and see the desert.

896
00:54:23,150 --> 00:54:24,390
You were still young.

897
00:54:25,590 --> 00:54:27,590
I didn't take your words seriously.

898
00:54:28,820 --> 00:54:29,930
But I was serious.

899
00:54:31,870 --> 00:54:34,260
When I secure my position as the Sword Wielder

900
00:54:34,260 --> 00:54:35,990
and the Gong family is at peace,

901
00:54:36,590 --> 00:54:38,320
I'll take you out to have a look.

902
00:54:39,520 --> 00:54:41,120
It's so cold at the back hill.

903
00:54:42,100 --> 00:54:44,560
You've been guarding here for so many years.

904
00:54:45,040 --> 00:54:46,370
It must've been lonely.

905
00:54:52,310 --> 00:54:54,440
Since I'm the guard of the Xue Lineage,

906
00:54:55,310 --> 00:54:57,640
the hustle and bustle of the outside world

907
00:54:57,790 --> 00:54:59,430
has nothing to do with me.

908
00:55:03,090 --> 00:55:04,750
Same goes for the Sword Wielder.

909
00:55:04,750 --> 00:55:07,310
Since you've taken on the task to guard the Gong family

910
00:55:07,310 --> 00:55:09,440
and shoulder the burden of the valley,

911
00:55:09,900 --> 00:55:12,100
you should also have a proper attitude.

912
00:55:12,960 --> 00:55:14,370
The promise you made with me

913
00:55:14,370 --> 00:55:16,410
is just a passing remark made by a child.

914
00:55:16,410 --> 00:55:18,910
But the promise that the Sword Wielder makes to the Gong family

915
00:55:18,910 --> 00:55:20,150
can never be changed

916
00:55:20,690 --> 00:55:21,890
and never taken back.

917
00:55:23,890 --> 00:55:25,740
You may have strong emotional attachments

918
00:55:25,740 --> 00:55:26,800
to the Gong family,

919
00:55:29,560 --> 00:55:30,590
but I'm but a nobody

920
00:55:30,590 --> 00:55:32,990
who has been looked down since I was a child.

921
00:55:34,810 --> 00:55:36,310
I've seen the women of the Gong family

922
00:55:36,310 --> 00:55:38,110
be trapped for their whole life.

923
00:55:40,550 --> 00:55:42,990
Although they may think they are happy,

924
00:55:45,470 --> 00:55:47,070
they are still birds in cages

925
00:55:48,620 --> 00:55:49,900
and fishes in the pond.

926
00:55:52,020 --> 00:55:54,020
I've seen the men of the Gong family,

927
00:55:54,980 --> 00:55:57,980
though they have the ability to fight against Wufeng,

928
00:55:58,660 --> 00:56:01,520
they only know how to cower in this corner of a valley

929
00:56:02,040 --> 00:56:04,040
and care only about their own peace,

930
00:56:05,550 --> 00:56:08,150
indifferent to the chaos in the outside world.

931
00:56:12,130 --> 00:56:12,760
So...

932
00:56:15,470 --> 00:56:17,130
I don't actually have a strong

933
00:56:18,220 --> 00:56:20,550
emotional attachment to the Gong family.

934
00:56:21,830 --> 00:56:23,930
You are no longer a 9-year-old child,

935
00:56:25,170 --> 00:56:28,170
but you are still saying nothing but immature things.

936
00:56:29,800 --> 00:56:31,730
Wufeng is strong and complicated.

937
00:56:32,090 --> 00:56:33,260
It's not something

938
00:56:33,540 --> 00:56:35,070
that can be shaken up easily

939
00:56:35,070 --> 00:56:37,330
with just a spurt of rashness or passion.

940
00:56:38,560 --> 00:56:40,490
Although the martial world is big,

941
00:56:41,770 --> 00:56:42,780
isn't this valley

942
00:56:44,530 --> 00:56:46,260
also part of the martial world?

943
00:56:47,550 --> 00:56:48,950
By guarding this corner,

944
00:56:50,390 --> 00:56:51,790
we are also protecting

945
00:56:51,790 --> 00:56:54,520
a glimmer of light and hope for the martial world.

946
00:57:00,030 --> 00:57:02,230
You're overlooking what's important.

947
00:57:02,380 --> 00:57:03,730
You see a dead leaf

948
00:57:04,210 --> 00:57:06,270
and think the whole tree is withered.

949
00:57:06,690 --> 00:57:08,020
This is narrow-minded.

950
00:57:09,320 --> 00:57:13,250
You have had your prejudice against the Gong family since you were a child.

951
00:57:13,250 --> 00:57:14,210
This prejudice

952
00:57:15,620 --> 00:57:17,700
is this dead leaf to you.

953
00:57:19,150 --> 00:57:20,470
Sword Wielder, you must've not

954
00:57:20,470 --> 00:57:23,330
tried to learn more about the Gong family, have you?

955
00:57:25,560 --> 00:57:27,420
Learn more about the Gong family?

956
00:57:31,270 --> 00:57:32,050
Did you just

957
00:57:32,930 --> 00:57:34,390
call me the Sword Wielder?

958
00:57:36,860 --> 00:57:37,550
I told you.

959
00:57:38,730 --> 00:57:39,930
If you pass the trial,

960
00:57:41,440 --> 00:57:43,370
you will be the Sword Wielder to me.

961
00:57:47,390 --> 00:57:47,950
But

962
00:57:48,370 --> 00:57:50,030
I just passed the first trial.

963
00:57:50,220 --> 00:57:52,280
There are two more trials ahead of me.

964
00:57:52,950 --> 00:57:54,680
They have nothing to do with me.

965
00:57:54,680 --> 00:57:55,600
In my heart,

966
00:57:56,210 --> 00:57:58,670
you are worthy of the title "Sword Wielder."

967
00:58:02,700 --> 00:58:03,560
What about you?

968
00:58:03,650 --> 00:58:04,820
He acknowledged you.

969
00:58:04,820 --> 00:58:06,020
Of course I would too.

970
00:58:06,250 --> 00:58:07,380
What's there to ask?

971
00:58:11,510 --> 00:58:13,110
I've always wanted to ask...

972
00:58:13,520 --> 00:58:14,570
who among you two

973
00:58:15,710 --> 00:58:17,770
is the guardian of the Snow Hill?

974
00:58:18,190 --> 00:58:19,130
Me, of course.

975
00:58:20,940 --> 00:58:23,140
It took you so long to ask this question.

976
00:58:23,940 --> 00:58:25,670
You're bad at reading the room.

977
00:58:27,790 --> 00:58:28,500
The person

978
00:58:29,910 --> 00:58:31,990
you promised to take and see the outside world,

979
00:58:31,990 --> 00:58:32,770
to the sea,

980
00:58:33,250 --> 00:58:34,250
to view lanterns,

981
00:58:35,120 --> 00:58:36,850
and see the desert, was also me.

982
00:58:39,890 --> 00:58:40,410
Heh.

983
00:58:41,570 --> 00:58:42,770
Men can't be trusted.

984
00:58:47,850 --> 00:58:50,020
I'm just a servant who grew up with him.

985
00:58:50,860 --> 00:58:51,990
Why else do you think

986
00:58:52,100 --> 00:58:53,500
it took me seven years to learn

987
00:58:53,500 --> 00:58:55,160
the Three Forms of Snow Saber?

988
00:58:55,540 --> 00:58:56,140
What about

989
00:58:56,380 --> 00:58:56,910
him then?

990
00:58:57,540 --> 00:58:59,050
How long did he take to learn it?

991
00:58:59,050 --> 00:58:59,710
Four years.

992
00:59:00,750 --> 00:59:01,780
Four years?

993
00:59:02,580 --> 00:59:03,910
That's not fast either.

994
00:59:04,240 --> 00:59:05,920
I thought he was gifted.

995
00:59:06,930 --> 00:59:07,990
He spent four years

996
00:59:08,400 --> 00:59:10,460
to create these three forms

997
00:59:11,300 --> 00:59:13,380
to replace the old Snow Saber forms.

998
00:59:14,070 --> 00:59:14,770
Gong Ziyu.

999
00:59:15,520 --> 00:59:17,180
You're now the Sword Wielder,

1000
00:59:18,060 --> 00:59:19,260
don't let your father

1001
00:59:19,260 --> 00:59:20,880
down.

1002
00:59:27,540 --> 00:59:28,400
My father

1003
00:59:29,600 --> 00:59:31,380
didn't have high hopes for me.

1004
00:59:33,190 --> 00:59:35,520
He put all his expectations on my brother.

1005
00:59:36,700 --> 00:59:38,160
I became the Sword Wielder

1006
00:59:38,650 --> 00:59:41,780
only because of the sudden situation in the Gong family.

1007
00:59:43,360 --> 00:59:44,160
You're wrong.

1008
00:59:45,730 --> 00:59:47,860
Your father has devoted himself to you

1009
00:59:48,420 --> 00:59:49,480
and had high hopes.

1010
00:59:50,460 --> 00:59:51,590
Jin Fan is the proof.

1011
00:59:53,490 --> 00:59:54,140
Jin Fan?

1012
00:59:55,380 --> 00:59:56,780
Didn't you find it weird?

1013
00:59:56,930 --> 00:59:57,990
In the Gong family,

1014
00:59:58,510 --> 00:59:59,840
only the Sword Wielder,

1015
00:59:59,870 --> 01:00:00,930
the Lineage Heads,

1016
01:00:01,110 --> 01:00:01,770
the Elders,

1017
01:00:02,100 --> 01:00:03,300
as well as the Young Lord in succession

1018
01:00:03,300 --> 01:00:04,310
are qualified to

1019
01:00:04,330 --> 01:00:06,060
have a personal Jade Guardian.

1020
01:00:07,020 --> 01:00:08,550
What was your status before

1021
01:00:09,140 --> 01:00:10,340
that could have allowed Jin Fan

1022
01:00:10,340 --> 01:00:12,740
to follow you around since you were a child?

1023
01:00:13,510 --> 01:00:15,110
Maybe it's because my father

1024
01:00:15,550 --> 01:00:17,500
wanted to arrange a Green Jade Guardian by my side

1025
01:00:17,500 --> 01:00:18,560
to keep an eye on me.

1026
01:00:18,850 --> 01:00:21,830
He's afraid that I will bring him troubles outside of the Gong family.

1027
01:00:21,830 --> 01:00:24,410
Do you really think an ordinary Green Jade Guardian

1028
01:00:24,410 --> 01:00:26,070
can know the content of the Trial of the Three Realms

1029
01:00:26,070 --> 01:00:26,930
to this detail?

1030
01:00:27,330 --> 01:00:28,570
What do you mean?

1031
01:00:30,020 --> 01:00:32,710
Those who are in the front hill are all Green Jade Guards.

1032
01:00:32,710 --> 01:00:33,450
Those in the Council of Elders

1033
01:00:33,450 --> 01:00:34,460
and the guards in the back hill

1034
01:00:34,460 --> 01:00:36,190
are the Yellow Jade Guardians.

1035
01:00:36,810 --> 01:00:38,260
Back then, the former Sword Wielder,

1036
01:00:38,260 --> 01:00:40,720
withstanding the pressure from the elders,

1037
01:00:40,780 --> 01:00:42,310
took great pains to get them to agree to

1038
01:00:42,310 --> 01:00:44,640
transferring to Jin Fan to be by your side.

1039
01:00:45,550 --> 01:00:47,950
The former Sword Guardian took your safety

1040
01:00:49,140 --> 01:00:51,470
as seriously as he did with the whole Gong family

1041
01:00:51,470 --> 01:00:53,390
and even the whole valley.

1042
01:00:58,130 --> 01:00:58,950
Jin Fan...

1043
01:00:59,900 --> 01:01:01,760
is really a Yellow Jade Guardian?

1044
01:01:02,210 --> 01:01:02,840
No.

1045
01:01:04,860 --> 01:01:06,330
He's a Red Jade Guardian.

1046
01:01:08,810 --> 01:01:10,090
He is the youngest ever

1047
01:01:11,350 --> 01:01:13,810
Red Jade Guardian in Gong family's history.

1048
01:01:20,220 --> 01:01:22,280
Are there really Red Jade Guardians?

1049
01:01:23,490 --> 01:01:25,380
I think the elders lied to us.

1050
01:01:25,850 --> 01:01:27,190
Red Jade Guardians,

1051
01:01:27,630 --> 01:01:29,920
to me, are just like Nuwa and Fuxi,

1052
01:01:29,940 --> 01:01:31,230
they are just legends.

1053
01:02:21,920 --> 01:02:23,320
Your father asked Jin Fan

1054
01:02:23,650 --> 01:02:24,650
to give up his position of

1055
01:02:24,650 --> 01:02:26,120
the Red Jade Guardian he achieved painstakingly

1056
01:02:26,120 --> 01:02:27,390
through the trials

1057
01:02:28,140 --> 01:02:30,790
to be demoted to the lowest-level Green Jade Guardian

1058
01:02:30,790 --> 01:02:32,720
to serve you since you were a child.

1059
01:02:33,140 --> 01:02:34,340
Can't this prove

1060
01:02:34,740 --> 01:02:36,670
your father had high hopes for you?

1061
01:02:38,820 --> 01:02:39,300
Come!

1062
01:02:39,490 --> 01:02:40,690
Let's play together!

1063
01:02:56,760 --> 01:02:57,540
Guardian Jin.

1064
01:02:57,540 --> 01:02:59,050
You've been guarding for a whole day.

1065
01:02:59,050 --> 01:03:00,250
Would you like to eat?

1066
01:03:05,140 --> 01:03:05,620
No.

1067
01:03:12,140 --> 01:03:14,540
In order to match your top-class guardian,

1068
01:03:15,390 --> 01:03:15,990
Gong Ziyu,

1069
01:03:16,930 --> 01:03:18,990
you need to be a top-class Sword Wielder too.

